Things that need to be done, either by us or someone else (contact us if you'd
like to help!), in no particular order.

Expand the coverage of the language in the code generator.

Recognize, report, and recover from more types of errors.

Build a wave viewer.  (Work under way - send mail to savant-devel@ececs.uc.edu
to get involved.)

Support interactive debugging.

Support VITAL and SDF.

Implement the VHDL PLI.

Support VHDL-AMS.

Start building a library of VHDL models with known status for Savant - 
status being if they analyze correctly, simulate correctly, etc.

Support sanity warnings (aka -Wall) to help stricten up code.
